like that, she will not be the same person.\\\"\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a box\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"the same person\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was part of the reason for the decisions Painter and his wife, former world 800m medalist Jenny Meadows, took when their highest-profile athlete picked up that knee injury.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jenny Meadows\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"the decisions\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"Painter\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2314}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"former world\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"their highest-profile athlete\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"that knee injury\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first thing they did was rule her out of the indoor season.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first thing\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"the indoor season\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, by the time the World Indoor Championships came around in March, she was running fast enough in training to potentially still have won gold despite multiple missed weeks.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2511}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"the Worl