dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caster Semenya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her final Olympic preparation\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 4002}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of this year has been about perseverance,\\\" says Hodgkinson.\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4199, \"end\": 4209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9215129988438528, \"rank\": 0.085171887162232, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4163}, {\"ngram\": \"perseverance\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not gone smoothly when I think about it.\", \"from\": 4211, \"to\": 4257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had a lot of challenges personally, on the track and off it.\", \"from\": 4258, \"to\": 4325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4274}, {\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4288}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To see it all come together in the last 10 days has been very satisfying.\", \"from\": 4326, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last 10 days\", \"from\": 4357, \"to\": 4373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have just worked hard, kept my head down and even when I was injured and out for a while, it felt like one thing after another.\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4439}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 4507, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 4523, \"to\": 4530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In those times you just have to be consistent, keep going and that's how I have got where I am.\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those times\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Missing indoors was a blessing in disguise, allowing me to put together solid back-to-back weeks, and we are seeing those results now.\\\"\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Missing indoors\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4643}, {\"ngram\": \"a blessing\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4658}, {\"ngram\": \"disguise\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4670}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 4714, \"to\": 4718}, {\"ngram\": \"those results\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Painter has also identified a noticeable positive change in Hodgkinson's demeanour in the build-up to these Paris Games.\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4825, \"end\": 4835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9215129988438528, \"rank\": 0.085171887162232, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Painter\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4772}, {\"ngram\": \"a noticeable positive change\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4821}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 4851, \"to\": 4863}, {\"ngram\": \"these Paris Games\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 4884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She recently revealed the comedown after her debut Olympics, where she won silver at Tokyo 2020, was so severe that she suffered some form of depression.\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 5039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the comedown\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"her debut Olympics\", \"from\": 4927, \"to\": 4945}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 4961, \"to\": 4967}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4976}, {\"ngram\": \"some form\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5024}, {\"ngram\": \"depression\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also thrust her into the limelight while still a teenager - something that she initially struggled to cope with.\", \"from\": 5040, \"to\": 5155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the limelight\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5077}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has been through some tough times the last couple of years but it's hard to come to terms with all that at a young age,\\\" says Painter.\", \"from\": 5157, \"to\": 5296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some tough times\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5195}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 5215, \"to\": 5220}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 5246, \"to\": 5251}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5280}, {\"ngram\": \"Painter\", \"from\": 5288, \"to\": 5295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We see it in football with young kids bursting on the scene.\", \"from\": 5297, \"to\": 5358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 5311, \"to\": 5319}, {\"ngram\": \"young kids\", \"from\": 5325, \"to\": 5335}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know Fergie [Alex Ferguson] was always really good at protecting Ryan Giggs in the early days and did not want him to have much attention.\", \"from\": 5359, \"to\": 5499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5374, \"end\": 5387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferguson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1362780609533018e-51, \"text\": \"Alex Ferguson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferguson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Ferguson\"}, {\"begin\": 5426, \"end\": 5436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Giggs\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Giggs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Giggs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Giggs\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early days\", \"from\": 5440, \"to\": 5454}, {\"ngram\": \"much attention\", \"from\": 5484, \"to\": 5498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly you have got all these people wanting to talk to you and money on the table for this, that and the other, and it can be daunting when you are trying to train and run.\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all these people\", \"from\": 5522, \"to\": 5538}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is starting to be more like the old Keely.\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the old Keely\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has definitely come to terms with things and she is a lot bubblier, happier and effervescent again.\\\"\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 5752, \"to\": 5757}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The proof is evident on the track where Hodgkinson is doing all she can to make the absence of America's reigning Olympic champion Athing Mu a moot point.\", \"from\": 5831, \"to\": 5985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5871, \"end\": 5881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9215129988438528, \"rank\": 0.085171887162232, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The proof\", \"from\": 5831, \"to\": 5840}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5864}, {\"ngram\": \"the absence\", \"from\": 5911, \"to\": 5922}, {\"ngram\": \"America's reigning Olympic champion\", \"from\": 5926, \"to\": 5961}, {\"ngram\": \"Mu\", \"from\": 5969, \"to\": 5971}, {\"ngram\": \"a moot point\", \"from\": 5972, \"to\": 5984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson has now run faster than Mu's lifetime best, with the American finishing way down the field on her only start sincefalling at the US Olympic Trials- a dramatic incident that ruled her out of defending her title.\", \"from\": 5986, \"to\": 6207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5986, \"end\": 5996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9215129988438528, \"rank\": 0.085171887162232, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 6021, \"end\": 6023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.6812310687910177, \"rank\": 0.4679307002469033, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}, {\"begin\": 6050, \"end\": 6058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999985952223004, \"rank\": 1.2757772621475955e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 6126, \"end\": 6143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_curling_trials\", \"s